title: The total package! Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Gorgeous 3-bedroom two-story house with a classic-style red brick exterior available for immediate move-in located in Avery Ranch!', "You'll love the excellent interior design with high ceilings, adorable fireplace, tile flooring, massive windows, and lovely light fixtures.", 'The kitchen is ready for you to create some wonderful meals with its fully equipped state-of-the-art appliances that include a gas stove, microwave oven, large double door fridge, and dishwasher.', 'Also included are a pantry and granite countertops.', 'The second floor is entirely outfitted with carpet flooring with the bedrooms featuring large windows, and closets.', 'Be sure to view the primary bedroom complete with an ensuite bathroom that boasts an awesome bathtub and a double vanity!', 'Convenient location off Avery Ranch Blvd, close to Kelly Reeves Athletic Complex, Amenity Center, Brushy Creek Lake Park, and so much more!', 'Avery Ranch has a majestic 18 hole golf course, tennis courts, hiking and biking trails, competitive swim team, tennis club, basketball courts, numerous pools, parks and playgrounds.', '**', 'In person tour required (no exceptions)', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 4235889)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
